* Nara Prefecture, Yamatokōriyama City, Yata-chō 965

=== Access ===
* From {{ill|lt=Kintetsu|Q1531085|WD=Q1531085|1=Kintetsu Railway}} {{ill|lt=Kintetsu Kashihara Line|Q2491066|WD=Q2491066|lt=Kashihara Line|1=Kashihara Line}} {{ill|lt=Kintetsu Kōriyama Station|Q6414349|WD=Q6414349|1=Kintetsu-Kōriyama Station}}, take a bus bound for "Yamato-Koizumi Station East Exit" or "{{ill|lt=Yatadera|Q1781626|WD=Q1781626|1=Yata-dera Temple}} Mae," alight at "Yokoyama-guchi," then approximately 6 minutes on foot.

